publicwhip.spmotion: *S1M-3453 Iain Smith: 10th Anniversary of Voluntary Organisations North East Fife—That the Parliament congratulates Voluntary Organisations North East Fife (VONEF) on its 10th Anniversary; recognises the valuable contribution VONEF has made to voluntary and community groups and individuals throughout north-east Fife, in particular its success in attracting funding support, and wishes VONEF continued success for the future.Supported by: Mr Jamie Stone*
S1M-3453 10th Anniversary of Voluntary Organisations North East Fife (lodged on 2 October 2002) Mr Keith Harding*
